headline: 34-year-old spent $16K to start a side hustle, built it 20 minutes at a time—now her business brings in up to $90K a month
summary: Julia Holden was in "survival mode" as a new mom when she started her business Sleepy Hat, a baby hat with an eye covering. Now, it brings in $90,000 a month.
